    <headline>Gale, yellow level, Andenes - Torsvaag, 31 March 12:00 UTC to 01 April 12:00 UTC.</headline>
    <description>From Sunday afternoon northwest near gale force 7, from early Monday morning west occasionally gale force 8. Monday afternoon decreasing.</description>
    <instruction>It is not recommended to be at sea in a small boat.</instruction>
